{"tid":2418090,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"Gundam Seed ED1 「あんなに一緒だったのに」 廣東話改詞","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T06:31:21.000Z","uid":385775,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"95f950174d1df9c94b19c52b378f4b350352349d","tid":2418090,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"原詞：石川千亜紀；作曲、編曲：梶浦由記；歌：See-Saw<br />\n原曲Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xIJh6gcyv_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxIJh6gcyv_U&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c49cd122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xIJh6gcyv_U</a><br />\n<br />\n改詞《友敵戰》：<br />\n<br />\n從對視裏猶喚叫親䁥憶記<br />\n往舊染紅夕照 勢色今已非......<br />\n<br />\n月色抵晚時 越是追憶少時<br />\n越會 徒令我心失救治<br />\n絕迹的友誼 絕滅不需置疑<br />\n絕處 留淚血沾濕戰衣<br />\n<br />\n如墓碑將銘你的名字<br />\n來重聚解述我的故事<br />\n獻上敬禮懶理敵我雙方有過對～峙<br />\n<br />\n＊從對峙裏猶喚叫親䁥憶記<br />\n往舊染紅夕照 勢色今已非<br />\n愛恨種長日縱想解凍卻失諸交臂<br />\n<br />\n盟友敵對無奈去挑選捨棄<br />\n縱欲語無話說 殺得偏性起<br />\n各自爆潛力各迫出各撒手鑭兵器<br />\n困身鬥相煎生與死＊<br />\n<br />\n熱火早慣常 熱烈高燒戰場<br />\n熱血 唯獨我心生怪象<br />\n藉一幅雪牆 寂寞攻心發涼<br />\n直教 皮肉結焦心結霜<br />\n<br />\n如墓碑將銘我的名字<br />\n從泉下聽著你的故事<br />\n概信永遠兩隔或會修補割席斷～義<br />\n<br />\nRepeat ＊<br />\n<br />\n任初心遠離 潛藏退避<br />\n現況味 哪再安寢暢寐<br />\n若一心渴求無煩惱唯獨戰死<br />\n<br />\n從對視裏猶喚叫親䁥憶記<br />\n往舊染紅夕照 勢色今已非<br />\n愛恨兩纏下兩俱傷兩錯手摧足臂<br />\n<br />\n盟友敵對無奈去挑選捨棄<br />\n縱欲語無話說 殺得偏性起<br />\n各自爆潛力各迫出各撒手鑭兵器<br />\n困身鬥相煎生與死<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n只根據前期情節為題材而改詞。"},{"pid":"4e6fa62dbe1730feabe466bba6047c71917c5c4a","tid":2418090,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"有冇機填埋invoke<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一響前奏已經開始hyper<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637ea62fc40731ae094231f6128ea41682ab2b8a","tid":2418090,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6fa62dbe1730feabe466bba6047c71917c5c4a","tid":2418090,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:04:22.000Z","msg":"有冇機填埋invoke<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一響前奏已經開始hyper<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"Seed 好多首都好好聽<br />\n其實自己都唔算gundam 鐵粉<br />\n要做下功課睇下首歌主題講咩<br />\n同有冇一啲經典情節作為題材<br />\n先知自己有冇靈感可以改到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ec56d331628557e2dd15b09ab1d6dd98f2d6bc","tid":2418090,"uid":48858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5X8-TA-cJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5X8-TA-cJak&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=7338a7ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5X8-TA-cJak</a><br />\n我諗起呢個"},{"pid":"7f2cc62eafa35164dd16c9f7f59dbde6592550ef","tid":2418090,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ec56d331628557e2dd15b09ab1d6dd98f2d6bc","tid":2418090,"uid":48858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5X8-TA-cJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5X8-TA-cJak&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=7338a7ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5X8-TA-cJak</a><br />\n我諗起呢個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"呢首都係好好聽<br />\n子瑩呢個廣東話翻唱版本<br />\n我諗係動漫同人詞係出名到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我唔敢挑戰呢首"},{"pid":"44b891141f32b974c52770e2ba5eb72a88675696","tid":2418090,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets